        <span>Good as a base for a landing page or small portfolio section.</span>
      </article>
    </section>

    <div class="actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary">Start editing</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary">Preview ideas</button>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
